[[size 125%]] **Addendum 01:** Discovery [[/size]]

SCP-8038 first came to Foundation attention on June 1st, 2022, when a Foundation webcrawler picked up possible anomaly keyphrases on a popular forum board dedicated to anime wherein fans of //Sparkling Butterfly// discussed a mysterious new 79th episode of the series. 
